snippet.title: The Behavior Panel
snippet.description:
We are four of the world's top body language and behavior experts; Scott Rouse, Mark Bowden, Chase Hughes, and Greg Hartley. Together as The Behavior Panel we analyze body language and human behavior in videos of public interest. We are non-partisan team, looking to educate and entertain you with our interest and expertise in communication, body language, deception detection, interrogation, and resistance to interrogation.

Watch our analysis of interviews with true crime, entertainment, and political figures. Learn alongside us how to detect truth, deception, and keep yourself and those you love safe. 

We post a new video every Thursday.
